1. Download better_figures.py and/or more_better_figures.py from this repository and make the toy figure more better!
What information do you need to convey? What colors will best convey the information, be easiest to see? What labels are needed?
What fonts? Where is the best placement for the legend? Make sure to check out the resources file in this repo.

2. Revisit one of the graphs you made in assignments one or two and make it better. Make sure it has titles and label its axes.
Adjust the colors. What else will make it easier to read? 

